, a strictly positive rate $R_0$\nis required for the relay channel capacity to be equal to the broadcast bound.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Feb 2016 00:56:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2016 18:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-31"}
