ated hadronic species that would potentially contribute to the\ndegradation of a sensor mounted in a precision sampling calorimeter. Depending\non sensor technology, efficient charge collection was observed for doses as\nlarge as 270 Mrad.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Feb 2016 05:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-01"}
